quran[6{c,v,t}:
3,181,"Allah ne unn logon ka qoul suna jo kehte hain ke Allah faqeer hai aur hum ghanni hain un ki yeh baatein bhi hum likh len ge, aur is se pehlay jo woh payghambaroon ko na-haq qatal karte rahay hain woh bhi un ke nama aamaal mein Sabt hai ( jab faisla ka waqt aeye ga uss waqt ) hum un se kahin ge ke lau, ab azaab jahannum ka maza chako"
3,182,"yeh tumahray apne hathon ki kamaai hai, Allah apne bundon ke liye zalim nahi hai"
3,183,"jo log kehte hain"" Allah ne hum ko hadaayat kar di hai ke hum kisi ko rasool tasleem nah karen jab taq woh hamaray samnay aisi qurbani nah kere jisay ( ghaib se aakar ) aag kha le "", unn se kaho,"" tumahray paas mujh se pehlay bohat se rasool aa chuke hain jo bohat si roshan nishanain laaye thay aur woh nishani bhi laaye thay jis ka tum zikar karte ho, phir agar ( imaan laane ke liye yeh shart paish karne mein ) tum sachey ho to unn Rasolo-n ko tum ne kyun qatal kya? """
3,184,ab ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam! agar yeh log tumhe jutlatay hain to bohat se rasool tum se pehlayjhutla-ay ja chuke hain jo khuli khuli nishanain aur saheefay aur roshni bakhsnay wali kitaaben laaye thay
3,185,"aakhir-kaar har shakhs ko marna hai aur tum sab apne apne poooray ajar qayamat ke roz panay walay ho kamyaab darasal woh hai jo wahan aatish dozakh se bach jaye aur jannat mein daakhil kar diya jaye rahi yeh duniya, to yeh mehez aik zahir fraib cheez hai"
3,186,"mslmano! tumhe maal aur jaan dono ki aazmayshin paish aa kar rahen gi, aur tum ahal kitaab aur mushriqeen se bohat si takleef da baatein suno ge agar un sab halaat mein tum sabr aur khuda tarsi ki rawish par qaim raho to yeh barray hosla ka kaam hai"
